## ğŸ§­ Epic 1: User Onboarding & Profiles

### 1.1 User Sign Up & Login
**Story**: As a new user, I want to sign up and log in so I can save my plans and preferences.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Email/password sign-up and login.
- OAuth via Google.
- Welcome screen with quick intro.

### 1.2 Profile Setup
**Story**: As a user, I want to set my dietary preferences and allergies so that my meal plan avoids undesired ingredients.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Form to select diet (e.g. vegetarian, vegan, keto).
- Ability to input allergies.
- Skill level selection.

### 1.3 Join or Create House
**Story**: As a user, I want to create or join a house so I can share meal plans with housemates.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Create a house with a name.
- Invite via link or house code.
- Join via invite or code.

