## ğŸ›’ Epic 4: Shopping List

### 4.1 Auto-Generate Shopping List
**Story**: As a user, I want a shopping list generated from my meal plan so I know what to buy.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Consolidated ingredients with quantities.
- Sorted by category (Produce, Dairy, etc.).
- Indicate storage type.

### 4.2 Mark Items as Purchased
**Story**: As a user, I want to mark items as purchased.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Checkbox toggle for each item.
- Visual indicator for completed items.

### 4.3 Assign Ingredients to Shoppers (Stretch)
**Story**: As a housemate, I want to divide the shopping list.  
**Acceptance Criteria**:
- Assign items to users.
- See my assignments in a filtered view.

